title: Chris Hardwick
description: Chris Hardwick (You know him! I know you do! Nerdist podcast! Comedy! SHIPMATES! (Seriously, Pete loves shipmates) comes by to FINALLY make it weird! And this one gets funny, weird, strange... sexy? I mean, what could we possibly mean by that? No idea. Just enjoy, you weirdos!!
